      "description": "The devil conjures a fiery chain to bind a creature.\n\nDexterity Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=9vCVJrzUZL0ra4w2]], [[lookup @target.affects.labels.statblock activity=9vCVJrzUZL0ra4w2]] the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can see within [[lookup @range.value activity=9vCVJrzUZL0ra4w2]] feet.\n\nFailure: [[/damage average]] damage, and the target has the &amp;Reference[Restrained apply=false] condition until the end of the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s next turn, at which point the chain disappears. If the target is Large or smaller, the devil moves the target up to 30 feet straight toward itself.\n\nSuccess: The chain disappears.",
